name: Kawakaze Diffusion
description:
This model was trained on the dataset with kawakaze images and then merged with other my models.

The model itself can produce other characters besides kawakaze, but sometimes there is a strong bias in the character traits, so I decided to name the model that way.

All images in the examples used lora with multiplier 0.4, this lora is in my profile.

And also, all the examples are made with multidiffusion, so the original seeds are lost.
